# Variation options — pipe-separated, in the order they should appear in the Etsy dropdown.
# Sizes and paper qualities listed here become the matrix of products in updateListingInventory.
# Every (size, paper_quality) combination must have a price in ETSY_PRICE_TABLE.
ETSY_SIZES=Digital Download|13×18 cm - 5×7”|15×20 cm - 6×8”|20×25 cm - 8×10”|21×29.7 cm - 8×12”|27×35 cm - 11×14”|28×43 cm - (11×17”)|A3 (29.7×42 cm)|30×40 cm - 12×16”|30×45 cm - 12×18”|40×50 cm - 16×20”|40×60 cm - 16×24”|A2 (42×59.4 cm)|45×60 cm - 18×24”|50×70 cm - 20×28”|A1 (59.4×84.1 cm)|60×80 cm - 24×32”|60×90 cm - 24×36”|70×100 cm - 28×40”|75×100 cm - 30×40”|A0 (84.1×118.9 cm)|25x25cm / 10x10"|30x30 cm / 12x12"|35x35 cm / 14x14"|40x40 cm /16x16"|45x45 cm /18x18"|50x50 cm / 20x20"|70x70 cm / 28x28"
# Comma is unsuitable here because quality names contain spaces and other separators.
# Pipe (|) is used as the separator. Pipe is not a valid character in Etsy variation values,
# so there is no risk of collision.
ETSY_PAPER_QUALITIES=Digital Download|Classic Semi-Glossy 170 GSM|Premium Semi-Glossy 200 GSM|Classic Matte 170 GSM|Fine Art 200 GSM|Museum Matte 250 GSM|Premium Matte 200 GSM
